==English==

===Verb===
'''zombify'''

# {{transitive}} To turn into a [[zombie]] - a living dead.
# {{transitive}} (''Of a PC computer'') To use as a [[zombie]] in order to disseminate [[spam]].
#: ''These [[trojan]]s can '''zombify''' your machine.''

